Second example using TensorFlow.JS and a pre-trained Mobilenet model from Keras


Preparing the three models...





Notes

This demo uses these pretrained models from Keras:

  • JSON model of the version 1. alpha 0.25 - you can see here
  • Packetized mobilenet version 1. alpha 1 - you can see here
  • Packetized mobilenet version 2. alpha 1 - you can see here

It is not trained to recognize human faces. For best performance, upload images of objects like piano, coffee mugs, bottles, etc. You can see all the objects types it has been trained to recognize in imagenet_classes.js.
